name: Meant4Rent
overview:
Apartments, houses, commercial spaces, and all other forms of Off campus housings for rent in Toronto, Ottawa, Vancouver, Calgary, Edmonton and many more Canadian cities. Meant4Rent is the first website to offer general renting along side with off campus housing and Free services for students to sell or buy textbooks near their schools. Find properties or textbooks near your location with the help of our fast and easy advanced search option and save all your searches for further comparison.

Post all your properties for a small fee (Guaranteed to never increase) fast and easy to University or College students. Meant4Rent is a user friendly website which can also be accessed easily by any smart phone. The site is simple to use and offers a lot of choices although they do provide fast response email support should you need it.

Don’t limit yourself, trust the right company to provide you with the best service with no hidden fees or contracts, and maximum security.

All in all, Meant4Rent is your #1 stop to rent and get your property rented as well as getting maximum exposure!
